### Calculator API — example requests
### Make sure the server is running first: uv run flask run --port 5001
### Then click "Send Request" above each block.

### 1. Help endpoint — should describe your API
GET http://127.0.0.1:5001/help


### 2. Add 3 + 9
POST http://127.0.0.1:5001/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "num1": 3,
  "num2": 9,
  "operation": "plus"
}


### 3. Multiply 7 * 6
POST http://127.0.0.1:5001/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "num1": 7,
  "num2": 6,
  "operation": "multiply"
}


### 4. Divide 8 / 2
POST http://127.0.0.1:5001/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "num1": 8,
  "num2": 2,
  "operation": "divide"
}


### 5. Edge case — divide by zero (should return 400 with error)
POST http://127.0.0.1:5001/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "num1": 10,
  "num2": 0,
  "operation": "divide"
}


### 6. Edge case — invalid operation (should return 400)
POST http://127.0.0.1:5001/calculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "num1": 1,
  "num2": 2,
  "operation": "banana"
}


### 7. Get full history — should now show all the calculations above
GET http://127.0.0.1:5001/history
